{"tid":1501032,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［Sir, this way］是旦哥:現存白宮聯署更新","createTime":"2019-08-24T08:32:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T18:40:13.000Z","uid":48912,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"8792a69aacbd896b3799fda7b9e5d39540e3bf5d","tid":1501032,"uid":48912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T08:32:22.000Z","msg":"幫是旦哥出post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PxD00Fh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPxD00Fh.jpg&h=4f385484&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/764219590311857/posts/2373594089374391?s=794244344&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F764219590311857%2Fposts%2F2373594089374391%3Fs%3D794244344%26sfns%3Dmo&d=mYJIHVlKms%2F2btm24%2BMsOg%2BnBs0jvEEXkL0KxwFTSeM%3D&h=6db9e5ee\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/764219590311857/posts/2373594089374391?s=794244344&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n【現存白宮聯署更新】<br />\n<br />\n明白現在實在太多白宮聯署，好多人會唔記得自己簽咗邊個，我有以下建議：<br />\n<br />\n1/ 唔肯定嘅，簽多一次。在我的道德標準下，呢個可以，因為你唔係故意用同一個電郵簽幾次。<br />\n<br />\n2/ 簽咗之後，自己mark返自己簽咗邊個，這是大家的責任。<br />\n<br />\n《未夠數》<br />\n==========<br />\n中國武警冒充香港警察，白宮聯署請求美國國會盡快通過香港人權民主法案 <br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2YW8pa8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2YW8pa8&d=mYJIHVlKms%2F2btm24%2BMsOg%2BnBs0jvEEXkL0KxwFTSeM%3D&h=f86c86af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2YW8pa8</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />請求美國取消中國學生簽證<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/30GcBMM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F30GcBMM&d=mYJIHVlKms%2F2btm24%2BMsOg%2BnBs0jvEEXkL0KxwFTSeM%3D&h=c2f06e65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/30GcBMM</a><br />\n<br />\n請求美國派美軍拯救香港巿民<br />\n <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2KsmYOQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2KsmYOQ&d=mYJIHVlKms%2F2btm24%2BMsOg%2BnBs0jvEEXkL0KxwFTSeM%3D&h=49640c1f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2KsmYOQ</a><br />\n<br />\n請求美國將中國共產黨定性為恐怖組織<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2MlpLM3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2MlpLM3&d=mYJIHVlKms%2F2btm24%2BMsOg%2BnBs0jvEEXkL0KxwFTSeM%3D&h=5ab9dc5a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2MlpLM3</a><br />\n<br />\n請求美國向北京施壓，停止製造白色恐怖<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2Zkc8hX\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Zkc8hX&d=mYJIHVlKms%2F2btm24%2BMsOg%2BnBs0jvEEXkL0KxwFTSeM%3D&h=2b38dfb9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2Zkc8hX</a><br />\n<br />\n拯救國泰航空，保障經濟自由<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2ZmWgPU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2ZmWgPU&d=mYJIHVlKms%2F2btm24%2BMsOg%2BnBs0jvEEXkL0KxwFTSeM%3D&h=bc8d432f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2ZmWgPU</a><br />\n<br />\n要求拒絕前警務處處長曾偉雄到聯合國就任提名<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2Z0cMkw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Z0cMkw&d=mYJIHVlKms%2F2btm24%2BMsOg%2BnBs0jvEEXkL0KxwFTSeM%3D&h=3fdce8c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2Z0cMkw</a><br />\n🇺🇸🇺🇸🇺🇸🇺🇸🇺🇸🇺🇸🇺🇸🇺🇸🇺🇸🇺🇸<br />\n《以下夠數，但到期前越多人越好》<br />\n==========<br />\n請求美國派出醫療船支援香港 <br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2H221Iu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2H221Iu&d=mYJIHVlKms%2F2btm24%2BMsOg%2BnBs0jvEEXkL0KxwFTSeM%3D&h=6b3d5009\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2H221Iu</a><br />\n<br />\n請求美國國會確認香港警察為恐怖組織 <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2KzVVQB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2KzVVQB&d=mYJIHVlKms%2F2btm24%2BMsOg%2BnBs0jvEEXkL0KxwFTSeM%3D&h=1f4d728f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2KzVVQB</a><br />\n<br />\n請美國國會提名【爭取民主自由的香港人】競逐諾貝爾和平獎，藉以保護義士<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2ZbGdQH\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3