us%2F1165517260749803526%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0qgGtzTXv7ZBHARA4cNQvLlkLI4ncvlCcEYGHwodS77eoppCIw6oBNkz8&d=mYJIHVlKms%2F2btm24%2BMsOg%2BnBs0jvEEXkL0KxwFTSeM%3D&h=67dac52b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FGlobalHimalaya%2Fstatus%2F1165517260749803526%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0qgGtzTXv7ZBHARA4cNQvLlkLI4ncvlCcEYGHwodS77eoppCIw6oBNkz8&h=a347f33e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/GlobalHimalaya/status/1165517260749803526?fbclid=IwAR0qgGtzTXv7ZBHARA4cNQvLlkLI4ncvlCcEYGHwodS77eoppCIw6oBNkz8</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n簽啦屌"},{"pid":"7b19cba25dbc809f2f073064731f65faa4ae8701","tid":1501032,"uid":48912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T09:34:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好意思借個位宣傳。<br />\n<br />\n可能因為大陸網絡攻擊，令到之前反對曾偉雄的白宮聯署停留在 77743 個簽名！請各兄弟重新簽署這個聯署！香港人心不死！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/we-demand-rejection-andy-tsangs-nomination-united-nations-positions-re-petition\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fwe-demand-rejection-andy-tsangs-nomination-united-nations-positions-re-petition&d=mYJIHVlKms%2F2btm24%2BMsOg%2BnBs0jvEEXkL0KxwFTSeM%3D&h=4e64b2a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/we-demand-rejection-andy-tsangs-nomination-united-nations-positions-re-petition</a><br />\n<br />\n大陸加強壓力打擊國泰，可能想低價從大股東太古手上收購股份！以政治壓迫航空公司，是恐怖主義行為！\u001d要求美國杯葛所有大陸的航空公司！請幫手聯署！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/aviation-safety-please-boycott-chinese-airlines-china-now-threatens-cathay-pacific-politics\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Faviation-safety-please-boycott-chinese-airlines-china-now-threatens-cathay-pacific-politics&d=mYJIHVlKms%2F2btm24%2BMsOg%2BnBs0jvEEXkL0KxwFTSeM%3D&h=e59fc73c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/aviation-safety-please-boy